flowchart TD

    A[Start Program] --> B[Initialize Game]
    B --> C[Create and Shuffle Deck]
    C --> D[Deal 2 Cards to Player]
    D --> E[Deal 2 Cards to Dealer]
    E --> F[Display Player Hand]
    F --> G[Display Dealer Upcard]

    G --> H{Player Turn}

    H --> I[Prompt: Hit or Stand]
    I --> J{Hit?}

    J -- Yes --> K[Deal Card to Player]
    K --> L[Adjust for Aces]
    L --> M{Player Bust?}
    M -- Yes --> N[Player Loses Round]
    M -- No --> H

    J -- No --> O[Dealer Turn Begins]

    O --> P[Reveal Dealer Hand]
    P --> Q{Dealer Total < 17?}
    Q -- Yes --> R[Dealer Hits]
    R --> S[Adjust for Aces]
    S --> Q
    Q -- No --> T{Dealer Bust?}

    T -- Yes --> U[Player Wins Round]
    T -- No --> V[Compare Hands]
    V --> W{Who Has Higher Total?}

    W -- Player --> U
    W -- Dealer --> N
    W -- Tie --> X[Push]

    N --> Y[Display Result]
    U --> Y
    X --> Y

    Y --> Z{Play Again?}
    Z -- Yes --> C
    Z -- No --> AA[End Program]